<p><a href="www.baidu.com">baidu</a></p>
<p>容器</p>
<p><code>&#123;% note class_name %&#125; Content (md partial supported) &#123;% endnote %&#125;</code></p>
<p>其中，class_name 可以是以下列表中的一个值：</p>
<ul>
<li>default<ul>
<li><div class="note default"><p>Content (md partial supported) </p>
</div></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>primary<ul>
<li><div class="note primary"><p>Content (md partial supported) </p>
</div></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>success <ul>
<li><div class="note success"><p>Content (md partial supported) </p>
</div></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>info<ul>
<li><div class="note info"><p>Content (md partial supported) </p>
</div></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>warning<ul>
<li><details class="note "><summary><p>waring</p>
</summary>
<p>Content (md partial supported) </p>

</details></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>danger<ul>
<li><div class="note danger"><p>Content (md partial supported) </p>
</div></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/384472746">友链教程</a></p>
